@startuml
title OCI Control Plane Deployment

actor User
participant "OCI API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "AI Orchestrator" as ORCH
participant "AI Capability Registry" as REG
participant "AI Runtime Service" as RUNTIME
participant "AI Security Service" as SEC
participant "AI Observability Service" as OBS
database "Autonomous Database" as ADB
participant "OCI Logging / Monitoring" as OCIOBS

User -> APIGW : Invoke platform API
APIGW -> ORCH : Forward governed request
ORCH -> REG : Resolve capability
REG --> ORCH : Candidate implementation
ORCH -> SEC : Check policy / authZ
SEC --> ORCH : Decision + scoped token
ORCH -> RUNTIME : Create / update run state
RUNTIME -> ADB : Persist context
ORCH -> OBS : Emit trace + event
OBS -> OCIOBS : Route telemetry
@enduml
